facts_and_links: {'Quotes': ["Ezra Laemmle, son of President of Laemmle Theatres, Greg Laemmle: [as this quote proceeds continuously, the film alternates between shots of interview with Ezra Laemmle and footage of Laemmle family members at Laemmle Theatres locations, with Ezra's comments in voiceover] You know, you're never going to go in and meet 'Mr. Subway,' or 'Mr. Wells Fargo.' Right? I think it's very cool to walk into Laemmle Theatres and see a Laemmle and know that it *is* a family business. It would be a sad day for there to be a Laemmle Theatres ran by someone with a business degree, who's just not at all connected to the family. I'd almost rather there not be a Laemmle Theatres than for there to be a Laemmle Theatres without a Laemmle.", 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt11743152/quotes/?ref_=tt_dyk_qu'], 'Connections': ['Features Easy Street (1917)', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt11743152/movieconnections/?ref_=tt_dyk_cnn']}
